<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Provisional NOC Letter - Multi Owner</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .page {
            background-color: white;
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .border-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px dotted #333;
            padding: 4px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .pattern-border {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border: 1px double #333;
            padding: 40px 50px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Standard Frame lines */
        .page::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            left: 5px;
            right: 5px;
            bottom: 5px;
            border: 2px solid #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .page::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            border: 4px double #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Standard Watermark */
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .watermark img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content-area {
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #000;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Standard Logo Section */
        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            height: 80px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .doc-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 12pt;
        }

        .ref-number {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .date-line {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-header {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Table Styling */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        table,
        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        th {
            padding: 5px;
            background-color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        td {
            padding: 5px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .col-sl {
            width: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .col-gst {
            width: 20%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .subject {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .salutation {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .digital-note {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .page {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
            }

            .pattern-border {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            table {
                font-size: 9pt;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="border-frame">
            <div class="pattern-border">

                <!-- Standard Watermark -->
                <div class="watermark">
                    <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Watermark">
                </div>

                <div class="content-area">

                    <!-- Standard Header Logo -->
                    <div class="logo-container">
                        <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Webel Logo" class="header-logo">
                    </div>

                    <!-- Document Header -->
                    <div class="doc-title">
                        Provisional NOC of IT/ITeS Renting (Application Number: <%= data?._application_number %>)
                    </div>

                    <div class="ref-number">
                        <%= data?._ref_number %>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Date -->
                    <div class="date-line">
                        Date: <%= data?._current_date %>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Applicants Details Table Loop -->
                    <div class="section-header">Applicants Details:</div>
                    <table>
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th class="col-sl">Sl No.</th>
                                <th style="width: 25%;">Applicants Name</th>
                                <th style="width: 50%;">Address</th>
                                <th class="col-gst">GSTN/PAN Number</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <% if (data?._applicants && data?._applicants.length> 0) { %>
                                <% data?._applicants.forEach(function(applicant, index) { %>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="col-sl">
                                            <%= index + 1 %>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>
                                            <%= applicant?._name %>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>
                                            <%= applicant?._address %>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="col-gst">
                                            <%= applicant?._tax_id %>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <% }); %>
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td colspan="4" style="text-align: center;">No applicant details found.
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <% } %>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>

                    <!-- Subject -->
                    <div class="subject">
                        Sub: Permission towards sublet of space of <%= data?._sublet_area_sqft %> sq. ft. super built up
                            area at <%= data?._space_description %>
                    </div>

                    <div class="salutation">
                        Sir,
                    </div>

                    <!-- Body Paragraph 1 -->
                    <p>
                        This has reference to your (self declaration letter with UDIN: <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._udin %>
                        </span>) regarding the permission for subletting the space to M/S <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                        </span> at <%= data?._space_description %>.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Body Paragraph 2 -->
                    <p>
                        We would like to confirm our ‘No Objection’ for sub-letting the <%= data?._sublet_area_sqft %>
                            sq. ft. space to M/S <span class="bold">
                                <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                            </span> for carrying out "<%= data?._activity_type %>" activities as declared by M/S <span
                                    class="bold">
                                    <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                                </span> vide their letter dated <%= data?._tenant_letter_date %>.
                                    Your Provisional NOC is effective from <%= data?._noc_start_date %> to <%=
                                            data?._noc_end_date %>.
                                            The NOC would lapse automatically as soon as the said tenancies are expired
                                            by influx of time or the same are determined earlier.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        You are advised to comply all legal formalities regarding agreement with your tenants and inform
                        NDITA about the existence of the said firm in Sector-V area.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        You will have required to pay permission fees @ Rs.<%= data?._permission_fee_rate %>/- per sq.
                            ft. (permission fees is subject to change from time to time) of the super built up area
                            along with applicable goods & services taxes to W.B.E.I.D.C. Ltd by the 7th day of every
                            calendar month. Such fees shall be paid in advance in every month, irrespective of your
                            receiving rent from the tenant and the non-payment of Permission fees or any kind of
                            non-compliance may cause automatic cancellation/withdrawal of the NOC granted.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Moreover, you are requested to inform us about the vacancy and fill up of premises within the
                        month of its happening otherwise permission fees will be charged upto date as mentioned in the
                        agreement without any reversal thereon.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Thanking you,
                    </p>

                    <!-- Standard Signature Block -->
                    <div class="signature-block">
                        <div class="sig-title">Authorised Signatory</div>
                        <div class="sig-title">For Managing Director, Webel</div>
                        <div class="digital-note">(This document is digitally signed and does not require physical
                            signature)</div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>